<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: #FFA500; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9em; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Subscription Paused</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= @customer.first_name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Your <strong><%= @plan.name %></strong> subscription has been paused.</p>
        
        <p>No worries! Your subscription will remain paused until you're ready to resume. You won't be charged during this time, and no orders will be created.</p>
        
        <p>When you're ready for your next delivery, simply resume your subscription from your dashboard.</p>
        
        <p>
          The Coffee Team
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Questions? Just reply to this email!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
